<entry stylesheet="matteroverdrive:info/styles/guide.css">
    <page class="padded-page">
        <title size="2" class="matter-text small-title">机器升级</title>
        <text class="matter-text text-block">大多数超能物质中的机器均可以被升级. 升级模块多种多样.
            从效率升级到速度升级.
            它们都是由[item name=upgrade]制作而成.</text>
        <recipe item="[item name=upgrade]"></recipe>
    </page>
    <page class="padded-page">
        <title size="2" class="matter-text small-title">速度升级</title>
        <text class="matter-text text-block">速度升级用于为机器提速. 它几乎能够在所有超能物质机器上使用.</text>
        <recipe item="[item name=upgrade meta=1]" style="float:left"></recipe>
        <details item="[item name=upgrade meta=1]" style="margin-left:16px;margin-top:8px"></details>
    </page>
    <page class="padded-page">
        <title size="2" class="matter-text small-title">能耗升级</title>
        <text class="matter-text text-block">能耗升级能够有效地减少超能物质机器的能量消耗.</text>
        <recipe item="[item name=upgrade meta=2]" style="float:left"></recipe>
        <details item="[item name=upgrade meta=2]" style="margin-left:16px;margin-top:8px"></details>
    </page>
    <page class="padded-page">
        <title size="2" class="matter-text small-title">故障保护升级</title>
        <text class="matter-text text-block">故障保护升级会降低发生故障的概率.
            它可以安装在[block name=replicator]和[block name=decomposer]上,
            以降低发生故障产出[item name=matter_dust]而非对应物品或[guide name=matter_plasma]的概率.</text>
        <recipe item="[item name=upgrade meta=3]" style="float:left"></recipe>
        <details item="[item name=upgrade meta=3]" style="margin-left:16px;margin-top:8px"></details>
    </page>
    <page class="padded-page">
        <title size="2" class="matter-text small-title">范围升级</title>
        <text class="matter-text text-block">范围升级会提升类似[block name=transporter]的机器的工作范围</text>
        <recipe item="[item name=upgrade meta=4]" style="float:left"></recipe>
        <details item="[item name=upgrade meta=4]" style="margin-left:16px;margin-top:8px"></details>
    </page>
    <page class="padded-page">
        <title size="2" class="matter-text small-title">储能升级</title>
        <text class="matter-text text-block">储能升级能够提升机器的内部能量存储上限.</text>
        <recipe item="[item name=upgrade meta=5]" style="float:left"></recipe>
        <details item="[item name=upgrade meta=5]" style="margin-left:16px;margin-top:8px"></details>
    </page>
    <page class="padded-page">
        <title size="2" class="matter-text small-title">高级速度升级</title>
        <text class="matter-text text-block">高级速度升级是速度升级的进阶版本.</text>
        <recipe item="[item name=upgrade meta=6]" style="float:left"></recipe>
        <details item="[item name=upgrade meta=6]" style="margin-left:16px;margin-top:8px"></details>
    </page>
    <page class="padded-page">
        <title size="2" class="matter-text small-title">物质存储升级</title>
        <text class="matter-text text-block">物质存储升级能够提升机器的内部物质存储上限.</text>
        <recipe item="[item name=upgrade meta=7]" style="float:left"></recipe>
        <details item="[item name=upgrade meta=7]" style="margin-left:16px;margin-top:8px"></details>
    </page>
</entry>
